Introduction

Yuisa is a Japanese trainee. She is a former member of Japanese girl group ＧＯＬ☆ＨＡＦ２.

In June 2023, she participated in HYBE and Belift Lab's girl group debut project called "R U Next?". She was eliminated in episode 3 after ranking 22nd place.
